			<description><![CDATA[<p>
HubSpot is looking for a <strong>technical lead to help recruit, mentor, and lead</strong> a small group of engineers. This is the first engineering team we have created outside of North America.<br />
<br />
Our development organization comprises many small teams working in concert to create <strong>world class web applications</strong> and services. We believe that small, empowered, and self-motivated teams can do big things. We are building exactly this kind of team in Dublin and need someone to run it.</p>
<p>
Technical leads at HubSpot are passionate, hands-on engineers who own and guide the direction of the products they are responsible for. They also help develop and train the engineers who report directly to them.</p>
<p>
We are looking for someone who is comfortable working with a variety of technologies on the web. Our stack is diverse and includes the following: <strong>Java</strong> (DropWizard), <strong>Python</strong> (Django), <strong>JavaScript</strong> (Backbone.js, CoffeeScript, jQuery), HBase, <strong>Hadoop</strong> (MapReduce), <strong>MySQL</strong>, and ZooKeeper.</p>
<p>
The ideal candidate has experience recruiting and leading teams and has successfully shipped web applications that have scaled to many thousands of users.</p>
<p>
Come help us build real products that thousands of customers depend on.</p>
<p>
We offer a <strong>very competitive salary</strong> + <strong>pre IPO stock</strong> + <strong>benefits</strong> + a cool culture to work and grown in.</p>
<p>
We are currently only processing applicants for candidates who have a valid EU visa or passport.</p>
<p>
We also are not accepting canddiates from recruitment agencies</p>
